{"url":"https://www.yutaka-unyu.co.jp/saiyo/recruit/detail/storyid/60/","html":"<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" xml:lang=\"ja\" lang=\"ja\">\n<head>\n\t<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\" />\n\t<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Style-Type\" content=\"text/css\" />\n\t<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Script-Type\" content=\"text/javascript\" />\n\t<title>募集要項｜採用情報｜豊運輸株式会社採用サイト</title>\n\t<meta name=\"Description\" content=\"4t・中型・大型ドライバーの採用を福岡でお探しなら、豊運輸で重量物・特殊品輸送のエキスパートになりませんか。豊富な車輌をもつ当社なら、4tドライバーから始めて、大型やトレーラーへのキャリアアップも可能です。\" />\n\t<meta name=\"Keywords\" content=\"4t,中型,大型,ドライバー,採用,福岡,運輸,輸送\" />\n\t<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"all\" />\n\t<meta name=\"Author\" content=\"一般貨物自動車運送事業 豊運輸株式会社 採用サイト\" />\n\t<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no\">\n\t<meta name=\"format-detection\" content=\"telephone=no\">\n\t<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"/saiyo/css/style.css\" media=\"all\" />\n\t<script src=\"/saiyo/js/jquery-1.9.1.min.js\"></script>\n\t<script src=\"/saiyo/js/rollover.js\"></script>\n\t<script src=\"/saiyo/js/heightLine.js\"></script>\n\t<script src=\"/saiyo/js/jquery.matchHeight.js\"></script>\n\t<script src=\"/saiyo/js/scrollsmoothly.js\"></script>\n\n\t<!--[if lt IE 9]>\n\t<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/saiyo/js/html5shiv.min.js\"></script>\n\t<![endif]-->\n\t<!--[if (gte IE 6)&(lte IE 8)]>\n\t<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/saiyo/js/selectivizr.js\"></script>\n\t<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/saiyo/js/respond.js\"></script>\n\t<![endif]-->\n\t<!--[if lt IE 7.]>\n\t<script defer type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/saiyo/js/pngfix.js\"></script>\n\t<![endif]-->\n\n\t<!-- Google Tag Manager -->\n\t<script>(function(w,d,s,l,i){w[l]=w[l]||[];w[l].push({'gtm.start':\n\t\tnew Date().getTime(),event:'gtm.js'});var f=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0],\n\t\t\t\tj=d.createElement(s),dl=l!='dataLayer'?'&l='+l:'';j.async=true;j.src=\n\t\t\t\t'https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtm.js?id='+i+dl;f.parentNode.insertBefore(j,f);\n\t\t\t\t})(window,document,'script','dataLayer','GTM-WQDGNHP');</script>\n\t<!-- End Google Tag Manager -->\n</head>\n\n<body id=\"require-page\">\n<!-- Google Tag Manager (noscript) -->\n<noscript><iframe src=\"https://www.googletagmanager.com/ns.html?id=GTM-WQDGNHP\"\n\t\t\t\t  height=\"0\" width=\"0\" style=\"display:none;visibility:hidden\"></iframe></noscript>\n<!-- End Google Tag Manager (noscript) -->\n<div id=\"container\">\n\n\t<header_tag></header_tag>\n<!-- // ここまでフッター -->\n\n\t<div class=\"pan\">\n\t\t<div class=\"inner\">\n\t\t\t<ul class=\"clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"/saiyo/\">HOME</a></li>\n\t\t\t\t<li><a href=\"/saiyo/recruit/list/\">募集要項</a></li>\n\t\t\t\t<!-- 募集職種 詳細ページの場合 -->\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"rt\">営業職</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t</div><!-- / .inner -->\n\t</div><!-- / .pan -->\n\n\t<div id=\"mainimg\">\n\t\t<div class=\"inner\">\n\t\t\t<h2><img src=\"/saiyo/img/mainimg_recruit.png\" alt=\"募集要項\" width=\"150\" /></h2>\n\t\t</div><!-- / .inner -->\n\t</div><!-- / #mainimg -->\n\n\t<div id=\"content\" class=\"clearfix\">\n\n\t\t<div id=\"main\">\n\n\t\t\t<div id=\"intro\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"inner\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"tit\">運転がお好きなら、他ではなかなかできない輸送にチャレンジしてみませんか。</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"desc\">豊運輸では各種ドライバーを募集しています。中型免許をお持ちであれば、4tドライバーからスタートし、入社後にその他の資格を取得してキャリアアップすることが可能です。</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div><!-- / #intro -->\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"detail-sec01\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"inner\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"detail-title\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"detail-title__inr\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"detail-title__icon\"><span class=\"icon-regular\">正社員</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"detail-title__ttl-sub\">久山営業所</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"detail-title__ttl\">営業職</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t<table class=\"tbl-base tbl-base--tbl01\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<th>勤務地</th>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>福岡県糟屋郡久山町久原2904-2（福岡インターすぐ近く）</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<th>給与</th>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>月収250,000円～300,000円</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<th>必要資格</th>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>普通自動車免許</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<th>学歴</th>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>不問</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<th>年齢</th>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>59歳以下<br />\r\n＊定年年齢が60歳のため<br />\r\n＊68歳までの再雇用制度あり<br />\r\n</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<th>勤務時間</th>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>8：30～17：00</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<th>休日</th>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>月間７日（日、祝、その他）<br />\r\n夏季・年末年始休暇<br />\r\n６ヶ月経過後、年次有給休暇10日</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<th>試用期間</th>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>6か月間<br />\r\n＊勤務の評価により期間短縮の場合有り</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<th>待遇</th>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>通勤手当支給（上限26,000円）<br />\r\n車通勤可（無料駐車場あり）<br />\r\n家族手当<br />\r\n社会保険完備（健康保険、厚生年金、雇用保険、労災保険）<br />\r\n定期健康診断<br />\r\n昇給あり<br />\r\n賞与（年2回）<br />\r\n退職金制度あり（勤続3年以上）<br />\r\n安全保護具及び制服貸与</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</table>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"detail-tel-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"detail-tel-wrap__inr\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"detail-tel-wrap__ttl\">お問い合わせ先</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"detail-tel-wrap__txt\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"detail-tel-wrap__txt__tel\">TEL：<a href=\"tel:092-976-1979\">092-976-1979</a></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"detail-tel-wrap__txt__tanto\">本社　採用担当 ； 篠田</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"detail-sec01-btn__box\"><a href=\"/saiyo/recruit/list/\" class=\"btn-base btn-base--arw02\"><span>一覧へ戻る</span></a></div>\n\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\n\n\t\t\t<!--豊運輸の魅力-->\n\t\t\t<div class=\"detail-sec02\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"inner\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"hl01\">豊運輸の魅力</h2>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"col-list col-list--col3 features-list clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"features-box clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"features-box__img\"><img src=\"/saiyo//img/img_cmn_features01.jpg\" alt=\"魅力1：やりがいと安定\" /></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"features-box__detail\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"features-box__ttl\">仕<span class=\"tb_600\">&nbsp;</span>事</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"features-box__txt\">重量物輸送だからこそ味わえる醍醐味と、長く働ける安定。</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"features-box clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"features-box__img\"><img src=\"/saiyo//img/img_cmn_features02.jpg\" alt=\"魅力2：居心地の良さ\" /></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"features-box__detail\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"features-box__ttl\">社<span class=\"tb_600\">&nbsp;</span>風</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"features-box__txt\">家族のようにあたたかい仲間。優しく思いやり溢れる職場。</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"features-box clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"features-box__img\"><img src=\"/saiyo//img/img_cmn_features03.jpg\" alt=\"魅力3：福利厚生と安全\" /></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"features-box__detail\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"features-box__ttl\">職場環境</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"features-box__txt\">スタッフが働いてくれることに感謝し、それに報いる体制。</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"features-btn__box\"><a href=\"/saiyo//features/\" class=\"btn-base btn-base--arw01\"><span>詳しく見る</span></a></div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\n\n\t\t\t<!--豊運輸の仕事を知る-->\n\t\t\t<div class=\"detail-sec03\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"inner\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"hl01\">豊運輸の仕事を知る</h2>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"col-list col-list--col2 workflow-list clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<li id=\"bnr-workflow--medium\"><a href=\"/saiyo//workflow/#typeA\">中型ドライバーの1日</a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<li id=\"bnr-workflow--large\"><a href=\"/saiyo//workflow/#typeB\">大型ドライバーの1日</a></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\n\n\t\t</div><!-- / #main -->\n<side_tag></side_tag>\n\n</div><!-- / #content -->\n\n<footer_tag></footer_tag>\n\n</div><!-- / #container -->\n\n\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\n\t(function () {\n\t\tvar tagjs = document.createElement(\"script\");\n\t\tvar s = document.getElementsByTagName(\"script\")[0];\n\t\ttagjs.async = true;\n\t\ttagjs.src = \"//s.yjtag.jp/tag.js#site=RiXIsxJ\";\n\t\ts.parentNode.insertBefore(tagjs, s);\n\t}());\n</script>\n<noscript>\n\t<iframe src=\"//b.yjtag.jp/iframe?c=RiXIsxJ\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\"\n\t\t\tframeborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginhe\n\n\n\n\n\n\t\t\tight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\"></iframe>\n</noscript>\n\n<script src=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/riot/2.6.7/riot+compiler.min.js\"></script>\n<script type=\"riot/tag\" src=\"/saiyo/tags/header_tag.tag\"></script>\n<script type=\"riot/tag\" src=\"/saiyo/tags/footer_tag.tag\"></script>\n<script type=\"riot/tag\" src=\"/saiyo/tags/side_tag.tag\"></script>\n<script src=\"/saiyo/tags/base.js\"></script>\n\n\n<script>\n\t$(function() {\n\t\t$('.recruit-sec01 li .recruit-box').matchHeight();\n\t\t$('.top-recruit-sec li .recruit-box').matchHeight();\n\t});\n</script>\n\n\n</body>\n</html>\n\n\n\n\n\n","finalUrl":"https://www.yutaka-unyu.co.jp/saiyo/recruit/detail/storyid/60/","rendered":false,"_cachedAt":"2026-06-22T20:32:33.517Z"}